ğŸ§ª Evaluation Process
Each model was evaluated using:

X_test â€“ the 15% test set held out after SMOTE

Accuracy Score â€“ calculated as the percentage of correct predictions

Confusion Matrix â€“ visual summary of classification results

MATLAB Snippet:
matlab
Copy
Edit
for i = 1:length(models)
    model = models{i};
    modelName = modelNames{i};
    X_test_table = array2table(X_test, 'VariableNames', model.RequiredVariables);
    predictions = categorical(model.predictFcn(X_test_table));
    acc = mean(predictions == Y_test_cat) * 100;
    accuracies(i) = acc;

    % Plot confusion matrix
    cm = confusionchart(Y_test_cat, predictions);
    cm.Title = sprintf('%s - Accuracy: %.2f%%', modelName, acc);
end
